{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-initials/task-4","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":["<p>Slušao sam zvuk i vežbao izgovor početne konsonante i sloga.</p>"],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"zh-a1-learn-initials","challengeType":24,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Da bi se izgovorio početni konsonant <span class=\"highlighted-text\">p</span>, stisnite usne snažno, pa ga pustite sa brzim i jakim izduvavanjem vazduha. Ovaj izduv vazduha je ono što čini <span class=\"highlighted-text\">p</span> različitim od <span class=\"highlighted-text\">b</span>, koji koristi istu poziciju usana, ali proizvodi zvuk polako bez izduvavanja vazduha.</p>\n<p>Trebalo bi da osećate kao mali eksploziv u ustima, i jasan protok vazduha koji možete osetiti kada stavite ruku ispred usta dok ga izgovarate.</p>\n<p>Kako je ranije pomenuto, ponekad se može čuti ova početna konsonanta izgovorena kao <span class=\"highlighted-text\">po</span>. Dodavanje jednostavnog završnog sloga <span class=\"highlighted-text\">o</span> čini ga lakšim za čuvanje/slušanje.</p>\n<p>Kada <span class=\"highlighted-text\">p</span> prati poslednje odeljke <span class=\"highlighted-text\">a</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">o</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">i</span>, na <span class=\"highlighted-text\">u</span>, dobija slogove: <span class=\"highlighted-text\">pa</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">po</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">pi</span>, na <span class=\"highlighted-text\">pu</span>.</p>\n<p>Kao što je sa <span class=\"highlighted-text\">b</span>, kada izgovarate ove slogove, lako spojite zvuk <span class=\"highlighted-text\">p</span> direktno na završne fraze bez pauza između njih. Jedina razlika će biti oblik usta koje napravite za svaku specifičnu završnu frazu.</p>\n<p>Pokušajte izgovoriti <span class=\"highlighted-text\">p</span> na ovim slogovima, a zatim koristite <span class=\"highlighted-text\">po</span> u različitim tonovima kao primer.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Pinyin</th>\n<th>Slova</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">pō</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">坡</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">pó</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">婆</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">pǒ</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">叵</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">pò</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">珀</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"Chinese Curriculum","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-initials/task-4"},"questions":[],"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company3-reception.png","characters":[{"character":"Wang Hua","position":{"x":50,"y":15,"z":1.4},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"ZH_A1_pinyin_initials.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":86.23,"finishTimestamp":103.55},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Wang Hua","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Wang Hua","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":1.62,"dialogue":{"text":"p","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Wang Hua","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":3.54,"finishTime":4.24,"dialogue":{"text":"pa","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Wang Hua","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":5.25,"finishTime":5.97,"dialogue":{"text":"po","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Wang Hua","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":7.23,"finishTime":8,"dialogue":{"text":"pi","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Wang Hua","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":9.27,"finishTime":10.02,"dialogue":{"